title: CyberLink Power DVD Ultra Deluxe 7 + KeyGen [TPB] [Starfighterxi
description:
PowerDVD is a video player product available from CyberLink. It enables the viewing of DVD movies on the user&#039;s PC. DVD backups stored on hard disk (created using software such as DVD Decrypter) can also be played. The player can also be used to play videos encoded with other codecs, for instance DivX and Windows Media Video.

PowerDVD features include:

    * Advance audio settings capabilities from surround sound to headphones
    * Dual display mode - Movie playback on two screens
    * Adjusting movie colors
    * Useful Quick Toolbar
    * Resume DVD Playback
    * Screen snapshots
    * Changeable skins
